    # Platform Monitoring API
    [![N|Solid](https://s3.amazonaws.com/wetfeetproduction/companies/thumb_media/14/original/unilever-logo_reasonably_small.gif?1348509554)](https://nodesource.com/products/nsolid)
    This API allows you to retrieve information about the Unilever Anypoint platform infrastructure - especially the Organizations, Environments under the organization, Applications inside the Environment. This API can also be used to query the Application statistics and status - so that we can use it to monitor the appication on the platform.
